BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_312816682@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260301T024740Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260304T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260304T230000
SUMMARY:Tororo Japanese & English Language Exchange @ Madison by Toronto B
 abel 
DESCRIPTION:TorontoBabel: Toronto's International Language Exchange\n**Tor
 onto Babel × Tororo Language Exchange** presents: **Japan Night!**\n\nA N
 ippon-inspired cultural and language exchange\, turning Madison Ave Pub in
 to a Japanese-inspired space where the lights\, music\, and energy transpo
 rt you straight to the heart of Tokyo\, Japan.\n\nWhether you’re here to
  practice Japanese or to join our usual Language Exchange for other Intern
 ational Languages\, everyone is welcome to come\, connect\, and enjoy the 
 night.\n\nGet ready for J-Pop and Anime Music playing all night long\, fun
  board games\, and a special Anime Cosplay Contest 🎶🎲\n\nGuests are 
 encouraged to dress up as their favorite anime characters (or come in Toky
 o street-wear) and fully lean into the theme. We’ll be offering small pr
 izes for the best cosplay costumes\, so bring the creativity and have fun 
 with it 🏆\n\n**What to Expect:**\n\n✅ Language Exchange 🇯🇵🇨
 🇦\n✅ Japan-Inspired Themed Atmosphere 🎌\n✅ DJ Keiko Ojima playin
 g tunes all night long 🎵\n✅ J-Pop & Anime Music All Night 🎶\n✅ F
 un Board Games 🎲\n✅ Anime Cosplay Contest + Prizes 🏆\n\n📍 14 Ma
 dison Ave\, Toronto\, ON M5R 2S1\n🗓️ Wednesday\, March 4\n🕖 7:00 P
 M – 11:00 PM\nPull up solo or with friends — everyone’s welcome 💬
 \n\n**About Tororo Japanese and English Language Exchange:**\nTororo Langu
 age Exchange is a Toronto-based language exchange community. They host mix
 ed-gender events on Mondays and women-only events on Fridays\, focusing on
  group conversations in a relaxed and friendly atmosphere. Through languag
 e and cultural exchange\, Tororo aims to create a safe and welcoming space
  where people can make friends comfortably.\n\nLink: [https://www.meetup.c
 om/north-york-international-friends-meetup-group/](https://www.meetup.com/
 north-york-international-friends-meetup-group/)\n\nTororoは、トロン
 トで活動するLanguage Exchange Groupです\n月曜日は男女混合
 、金曜日は女性限定のイベントを開催しています。\nグ
 ループトークを中心に、会話や交流を楽しむリラック
 スした雰囲気の集まりです。\n言語や文化を通じて、安
 心・安全に友達を作れる場所を目指しています\n\n**Pleas
 e Note:** This is a language exchange and social event for practicing lang
 uages and making new friends only. We are not a dating or matchmaking even
 t. Harassment or inappropriate behavior of any kind will not be tolerated.
  Photos may be taken for social media—please inform the organizers if yo
 u’d prefer not to appear.\n\n💵 **$5 Entry Donation**\nYour contributi
 on helps cover our meetup fees\, name tags\, games\, stickers\, and all th
 e little things that make the magic happen.\n\n🔗 Meetup: [http://www.me
 etup.com/TorontoBabel](http://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel)\n📘 Facebook:
  [https://www.facebook.com/groups/torontobabel](https://www.facebook.com/g
 roups/torontobabel)\n💬 WhatsApp: [https://chat.whatsapp.com/EYMdUw8XaxE
 5irFSNg5bt7](https://chat.whatsapp.com/EYMdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7)\n\n👉 Che
 ck out the calendar to see what other events we have coming up and to RSVP
 .\n\n#TorontoBabel #LanguageExchange #TorontoEvents #ToDoToronto #LearnEng
 lish #LearnJapanese
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/torontobabel/events/312816682/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260110T130215Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260110T130215Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313055109@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260301T024740Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260318T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260318T230000
SUMMARY:Language Exchange & Social Event @ Madison Ave Pub by Toronto Babe
 l
DESCRIPTION:TorontoBabel: Toronto's International Language Exchange\nWe’
 re back for another night of great conversation\, community\, and global c
 onnections. Whether you want to practice English\, learn a new language\, 
 or simply make new friends from around the world\, this is the place to be
 !\n\n✨ **What to Expect:**\n✅ Language Exchange 💬 – chat in Frenc
 h\, Spanish\, Korean\, Japanese\, and more!\n✅ Live Music & Resident DJ 
 🎵 – groove while you mingle\n✅ Fun Board Games 🎲 – challenge a
  new friend\n✅ Arts & Crafts 🎨 – get creative\n✅ Make New Friends
  🗣️ – the more\, the merrier!\n\n📍 14 Madison Ave\, Toronto\, ON
  M5R 2S1\n🕖 7:00 PM – 11:00 PM\n\nCome solo or bring a friend—eithe
 r way\, you’ll leave with new connections\, good laughs\, and even bette
 r vibes 💬✨🫶\n\n💵 $5 Entry Fee at the Door\nThis helps cover mee
 tup essentials like games\, name tags\, stickers\, and all the little thin
 gs that make our events magical ✨\n\n**CONTACT:** Terry (Organizer)\n
 📲 E-transfer also available: tmg8@wealthsimple.me\n🔗 Meetup: [https:
 //www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel)\n📘 
 Facebook: [https://www.facebook.com/groups/torontobabel](https://www.faceb
 ook.com/groups/torontobabel)\n💬 WhatsApp: [https://chat.whatsapp.com/EY
 MdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7](https://chat.whatsapp.com/EYMdUw8XaxE5irFSNg5bt7)\n
 📸 Instagram: [https://www.instagram.com/t.o.babel](https://www.instagra
 m.com/t.o.babel)\n\n👉 Check out our calendar to see what other events w
 e have coming up and to RSVP:\n[https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#calen
 dar](https://www.meetup.com/TorontoBabel/#calendar)\n\n**Note:** Toronto B
 abel is a friendly\, welcoming\, and safe space for all attendees. This is
  a language-focused event and not a dating or matchmaking event. Any form 
 of harassment or inappropriate behavior will not be tolerated. If you expe
 rience or witness any issues\, please inform one of the organizers.\n\n#To
 rontoBabel #LanguageExchange #TorontoEvents #ToDoToronto #LearnEnglish
